lved over time. This capability is particularly impactful in managing chronic diseases, mental health dialogues, and polypharmacy scenarios where small shifts in language signal significant clinical changes. By embedding pragmatic reasoning into a longitudinal, verifiable memory structure, PMGN advances beyond single-turn disambiguation toward truly context-aware, trustworthy AI in healthcare.",
